### Variables (shared across all .http files)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@accessToken = 
@videoSourceId = 

### ─── Reports (Public) ───

### Report broken link (public, no auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/broken-link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoSourceId": "{{videoSourceId}}"
}

### ─── Reports (Admin) ───

### List broken link reports (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/broken-links?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
